\ex\label{ex:GRM-adj-mann-alot-n}

\gll dúó tʃʊ̄ɔ̄ɪ̀ kɪ́ŋkāŋ wà wíré\\
asleep lie.{\nmlz} {\dxm} {\neg} good\\
