\gll à kùórù ŋmá dɪ́ ʊ̀ bááŋ káá sīī [ǹ̩ nɪ́] rē\\
{\art} chief say {\comp} {\sc 3sg.poss} temper {\egr} raise {\sc 1.sg} {\postp}
{\foc}\\
\glt  `The chief told me that he was very angry with me.' 


